    "en": {
      "title": "35,000 MT of Petrol unloaded tonight (30)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Minister of power and Energy Kanchana Wijesekara says that the distribution lapses have been rectified & more stocks have been dispatched in the last 4 days.",
        "He said that Ceylon Petroleum Storage Terminals Limited (CPSTL) will continue to distribute 4000MT Diesel & 3000MT Petrol daily.",
        "\"Requirements for buses & school services have been full filled\", Minister Wijesekara said.",
        "Also, he said that another 35,000MT Petrol 92 cargo will unload tonight (30).",
        "If APG is not possible, next alternative is an Election: Maithree"
